org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.sql
Class AeQueryRunner

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.commons.dbutils.QueryRunner
      org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.sql.AeQueryRunner
public class AeQueryRunner
extends org.apache.commons.dbutils.QueryRunner

Extends the Commons DbUtils QueryRunner to handle Document parameters as character streams and to allow specifying the SQL type of null parameters.
